metadata.description: Today is Trans Day of Visibility 2023. i am a trans man so therefore i would like to participate. this is CENTIPEDE, a lil interlude that i started in 2022 around the summertime (first vocal track was recorded June 29th, 2022). the song was originally written with the beat and a topline, few lyrics except for "centipede and the butterflies" freestyled and the story came later. it was originally about the duality of life and a motivating song to keep pushing forward and the universe is a reflection of your internal world. it still is but as time has progressed it shifted from being a message to my nephews and niece to my internal struggle with fitting into society and being accepted as a trans person. so i felt it was right to be visible, take up space, and be myself.

lyrics.text:
centipedes 
and the butterflies are flying
so high in september skies
inspiring me
makes you go outside
and start crying
cause they know 
what we don’t 
ooooooo

so centipedes and the butterflies 
stay flying
keep feeding your 
living hearts desires 
need something stronger?
look alive, love.
it’s inside you.
